A modern white floral bouquet (jasmine, orange blossom) underlined with juicy notes of mandarin, reveals the seductress found in every woman. name: Steamer leather travel bag
description: A lovely Louis Vuitton steamer 35 travel bag in monogram canvas and natural tan leather, made in France in the early quarter of the 20th century. Steamer bags have been produced by Louis Vuitton for over 120 years. In 1901, the company introduced the simple canvas and leather steamer bag, whose squat, squarish proportions were based on the mailbags used in the Americas. Here was a bag that could be hung on the back of a cabin door, carried around on deck or stored away in the hold inside one of Louis Vuitton’s famous packing cases. The design has remained basically unchanged since then, as popular now as they were then. A nice piece for the seasoned collector. Sale number 891985. One side strap is missing. Heave leather wear throughout.

Christian Louboutin's 'Louix Ray' sneakers are a toughened-up take on the designer's signature high-top style. They're made using PVC that has a smoky, transparent appearance and detailed all over with spiked embellishments.  As a brand, Christian Louboutin is synonymous with elegance, technical proficiency, and of course, that iconic red sole.  Elevate your ultra-luxury sneaker game with the Christian Louboutin Arpoador Mesh & Suede Sneaker - a versatile and luxurious addition to any wardrobe.

BRAZILIAN BY NAME, COOL BY NATURE:  Born from Christian’s enduring love of Brazil and named after the iconic rock and surf spot situated between the beaches of Copacabana and Ipanema, the new Arpoador sneaker is the latest style to join the Maison’s iconic sneaker collection. And while its versatile dynamic silhouette nods to the graceful movements of Capoeira and the contours of renowned Brazilian architect Oscar Niemeyer's work, its complex technical construction has Christian Louboutin written all over it.

STAND OUT IN STYLE:  whether dressed up or dressed down, there's an Arpoador out there for every personality. First launched worldwide in our iconic Louboutin red, the latest addition to their sneaker collection now comes in a variety of colors, for both men and women.

name: Linen mini dress
description:
Doen Peony Ruffle Dress in Salt White Romantic Boho Fairy Womens Small

This gorgeous “salt white” mini dress deserves to be worn on an ice cream date or to frolic in a field. It’s fun, it’s flirtatious, it’s romantic. 

Made with Ramie fabric, also known as grass linen - a natural, sustainable, renewable material that comes from the nettle plant family. It's perfect for warm and humid climates - soft to the touch and breathable, sweat and moisture wicking, strong even when wet, dries quickly, and naturally resistant to stains, bacteria, and shrinkage.

An asymmetrical button front framed with picot-edged ruffles and pintucks makes a dreamy combination. Shoulder snaps and an adjustable tie-waist allow for easy on-off and personalized fit.

Armpit-armpit: 17.75”
Length: 33”

Pictured on Emily Schuman of “Cupcakes and Cashmere” and waiting to be worn to your next garden party.
